Nic Newling struggled through the confusing highs and lows of an undiagnosed bipolar disorder between the ages of 13 and 18 .
The 28-year-old moved between doctors and psychiatric wards and was fed various concoctions of prescriptive medication before finally being diagnosed with bipolar disorder .
Nic's brother, Christopher, was not as open about his emotions and depression as his older brother, Ben .
His death came as a shock to the family who had been focusing on Nic's mental health .